Outer garment, cloak, mantle, robe</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">References:</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">כְּסוּת</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(ksuth)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut22:12\">DEU 22:12</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">מַחֲלָצוֹת</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(machalatsah)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa3:22\">ISA 3:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech3:4\">ZEC 3:4</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">מִטְפַּחַת</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(mitpachath)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth3:15\">RUT 3:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa3:22\">ISA 3:22</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">מְעִיל</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(m‘il)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam2:19\">1SA 2:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam15:27\">1SA 15:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam18:4\">1SA 18:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam24:5\">1SA 24:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam24:12\">1SA 24:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam24:12\">1SA 24:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam28:14\">1SA 28:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam13:18\">2SA 13:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr15:27\">1CH 15:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra9:3\">EZR 9:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra9:5\">EZR 9:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job1:20\">JOB 1:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job2:12\">JOB 2:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job29:14\">JOB 29:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps109:29\">PSA 109:29<